description:
This is the additional puzzle pack for "Jigsaw Masterpieces 2". The following 10 moving puzzles are included.
-Yufuin in spring
-Bridge over the Shirasu River Estuary
-Hida Takayama in autumn leaves
-Tadamigawa River in snow
-Joganji River in fresh green
-Bridge overlooking the Watarase River
-Mt, Fuji and Astragalus field
-Canola field in Ishigami
-Train along the Tadami River
-Line cruising in Nagatoro
name: [Moving] Unexplored Train in Japan
